notes: House of Lords Library has items I and II only (not the letter).
description: Letter dated 31/05/2007 from Harriet Harman MP to Keith Vaz MP regarding appointment of Deputy Lieutenants and ethnic and gender monitoring statistics. 30 p. Includes I. Table showing ethnicity and gender statistics for Deputy Lieutenants as at the end of April 2007. II. List of Deputy Lieutenants for England at May 2007
